---
title: Chipotle Beef and Black Bean Tacos with Limey Avocado
description: These Beef and Black Bean Tacos are bursting full of flavours and make the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chipotle-beef-and-black-bean-tacos-fdfdb249-8cc2233a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chipotle-beef-and-black-bean-tacos-5e219ca2bcb0bb76a531bac5-617f6d73.pdf
